(261, 1, '2016-02-11 12:19:41', '2016-02-11 12:19:41', '<div class="faq marginBottom50">\r\n<div class="container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">\r\n<div class="faq-area">\r\n<h1>FAQ on Cheap Raffle Tickets</h1>\r\n<h3>About Raffle Ticket Orders</h3>\r\n<h4>Track Shipping</h4>\r\nTrack Shipping: You will receive an email with a tracking number the day your order is shipped.\r\n<h4>Post office Box Deliveries</h4>\r\nPost office Box Deliveries: UPS will not deliver to Post Office Boxes. We can, however ship your raffle tickets via U.S. Priority mail. The charge for priority mail is $5.00 per 1000 raffle tickets. Add the appropriate charge in the box: “Price for Additional Services add to my order”.\r\n<h4>Starting number for raffle tickets</h4>\r\nStarting number for raffle tickets: Unless you specify otherwise they will start at 001. You can specify to begin at 000 (lottery raffles) or any thousand increments such as 2001 or 3,001, etc. If reordering, specify the starting number in the “comments” section.\r\n<h4>Online Proof</h4>\r\nOnline Proof: Our online proof is there to give you an idea what your tickets will look like. If you’re not happy with the proof just tell us to send an actual proof (Our Artists have a lot more flexibility then the online proofing). If you’re adding a logo there is no need to request […]\r\n<h4>Reorders</h4>\r\nReorders: If you need more raffle tickets for an order you have place recently, that’s a pretty good problem to have. During business hours (Monday thru Friday and 10am to 1pm Saturday – EST) just give us a call (513)-733-3900. After business hours you can place online – you only need to fill in the […]\r\n<h4>Raffle Tickets really fast</h4>\r\nRaffle Tickets really fast: Depending on when we receive your order, your raffle tickets will ship free the same or next business day.** You can select from Free Ground Shipping, Next Day and 2 Day air on the Shipping page.\r\n<h4>Stapling and Padding</h4>\r\nStapling and Padding: The charge for stapling in increments of 5,10,15,20 or 25 is $.06 per book. The charge for stapling into books of any other increment is $.09 per book. (Padding the raffle tickets is cheaper than stapling and makes it easy for you to divide into small groups.) * We’ve created a quick […]\r\n<h4>Printing raffle tickets on the back</h4>\r\nPrinting raffle tickets on the back: The price is $15 per 1000 raffle tickets. If you want a logo or artwork printed on the back of the raffle tickets upload your artwork with your order and enter “print logo on back”: in the “back lines” section. You will receive an email proof before your raffle […]\r\n<h4>Can I add Artwork or a Logo?</h4>\r\nCan I add Artwork or a Logo? No problem, it only adds $10.00 to the price. Your artwork or logo should be at least 300 dpi. Upload your artwork with your order. You will receive an email proof before your Cheap Raffle Ticket Printing are printed.\r\n<h4>Different Stub Lines</h4>\r\nDifferent Stub Lines: No problem, no extra charge, just indicate what you would like in the “comments” section.\r\n<h4>Custom Ticket Printing</h4>\r\nCustom Ticket Printing: If you need a different color of paper stock, ink(s) or size contact us for pricing information.\r\n<h4>Different Colors or Size</h4>\r\nDifferent Colors or Size: Our standard tickets are printed in black ink on yellow 90 lb index card stock. They measure 2 1/8″ by 5 1/2″ with the stub 1 1/2″ from the left. We also offer White, Blue and Green card stock at no additional charge. If you would like your tickets printed in […]\r\n<h4>Admission tickets</h4>\r\nAdmission tickets are essentially the same as raffle tickets in that they have consecutive numbers on each end but they do not have a stub. Pricing is the same. You can request us to change the stub ie, instead of Name, Address and Phone ADMIT ONE, name and date of your event. (This is helpful […]\r\n<p class="param-area-bar">I have questions about my raffle ticket order. How can I reach you by phone? (513) 733-3900\r\nWe are open weekdays 9am to 5:30pm, Monday thru Friday and 10am to 1pm Saturday (Eastern Standard Time).</p>\r\n<p class="param-area-bar-2">* Orders requiring approval of proof or extra production time will delay shipping of your raffle tickets approximately 1 day.</p>\r\n<p class="param-area-bar-3">* Business days are normal UPS Ground Shipping Days. We are not responsible for delays due to circumstances beyond our control.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'FAQ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '260-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-11 12:19:41', '2016-02-11 12:19:41', '', 260, 'http://www.raffle.dev/260-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
