ld you like to sell? Make definite plans for when and where you will go out selling.\r\n\r\nYou have to tell people about the raffle to sell raffle tickets! Talk about the event to friends, family members, and neighbors. When someone says, “What’s new?” tell the person that you’re selling raffle tickets. Talk about your organization, what its goals are, and what the money will be used for.\r\n\r\nAsk for the sale. Sincerity is the only key ingredient you need. If you believe in your cause, your cause will sell itself. All you have to do is say, “Hey, you want to buy some raffle tickets?”', 'Raffle Sales Tips', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '387-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:10:38', '2016-02-25 12:10:38', '', 387, 'http://www.raffle.dev/387-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
