(399, 1, '2016-02-25 12:14:58', '2016-02-25 12:14:58', 'Admission tickets are essentially the same as raffle tickets in that they have consecutive numbers on each end but they do not have a stub. Pricing is the same.\r\nYou can request us to change the stub ie, instead of Name, Address and Phone ADMIT ONE, name and date of your event. (This is helpful if you are pre-selling your tickets because your seller can retain the stub portion for record keeping. If you prefer no stub, place your order and select “tickets with no stub”. In either case, your proof will show a standard stub but your Admission Tickets will either have no stub or one with the information you requested.', 'Admission tickets', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'admission-tickets', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:14:58', '2016-02-25 12:14:58', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=399', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(400, 1, '2016-02-25 12:15:36', '2016-02-25 12:15:36', 'Different Colors or Size: Our standard tickets are printed in black ink on yellow 90 lb index card stock. They measure 2 1/8″ by 5 1/2″ with the stub 1 1/2″ from the left. We also offer White, Blue and Green card stock at no additional charge. If you would like your tickets printed in one of these colors just let us know in the “comments” section.', 'Different Colors or Size', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'different-colors-or-size', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:15:36', '2016-02-25 12:15:36', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=400', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(401, 1, '2016-02-25 12:16:28', '2016-02-25 12:16:28', 'Custom Ticket Printing: If you need a different color of paper stock, ink(s) or size contact us for pricing information', 'Custom Ticket Printing', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'custom-ticket-printing', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:16:28', '2016-02-25 12:16:28', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=401', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(402, 1, '2016-02-25 12:16:53', '2016-02-25 12:16:53', 'Different Stub Lines: No problem, no extra charge, just indicate what you would like in the “comments” section.\r\n', 'Different Stub Lines', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'different-stub-lines', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:16:53', '2016-02-25 12:16:53', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=402', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(403, 1, '2016-02-25 12:17:08', '2016-02-25 12:17:08', 'Can I add Artwork or a Logo? No problem, it only adds $10.00 to the price. Your artwork or logo should be at least 300 dpi. Upload your artwork with your order. You will receive an email proof before your Cheap Raffle Ticket Printing are printed.', 'Can I add Artwork or a Logo?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'can-i-add-artwork-or-a-logo', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:17:08', '2016-02-25 12:17:08', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=403', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(404, 1, '2016-02-25 12:17:27', '2016-02-25 12:17:27', 'Printing raffle tickets on the back: The price is $15 per 1000 raffle tickets. If you want a logo or artwork printed on the back of the raffle tickets upload your artwork with your order and enter “print logo on back”: in the “back lines” section. You will receive an email proof before your raffle tickets are printed.', 'Printing raffle tickets on the back', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'printing-raffle-tickets-on-the-back', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:17:27', '2016-02-25 12:17:27', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=404', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(405, 1, '2016-02-25 12:18:15', '2016-02-25 12:18:15', 'Stapling and Padding: The charge for stapling in increments of 5,10,15,20 or 25 is $.06 per book. The charge for stapling into books of any other increment is $.09 per book. (Padding the raffle tickets is cheaper than stapling and makes it easy for you to divide into small groups.) * We’ve created a quick video to explain the difference between stapling and padding – have a look: Stapling and padding', 'Stapling and Padding', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'stapling-and-padding', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:18:15', '2016-02-25 12:18:15', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=405', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(406, 1, '2016-02-25 12:18:25', '2016-02-25 12:18:25', 'Raffle Tickets really fast: Depending on when we receive your order, your raffle tickets will ship free the same or next business day.** You can select from Free Ground Shipping, Next Day and 2 Day air on the Shipping page.', 'Raffle Tickets really fast', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'raffle-tickets-really-fast', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:18:25', '2016-02-25 12:18:25', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=406', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(407, 1, '2016-02-25 12:18:36', '2016-02-25 12:18:36', 'Reorders: If you need more raffle tickets for an order you have place recently, that’s a pretty good problem to have. During business hours (Monday thru Friday and 10am to 1pm Saturday – EST) just give us a call (513)-733-3900. After business hours you can place online – you only need to fill in the first ticket line. In the “instructions” section tell us that this is an exact reorder and what number to start at.', 'Reorders', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'reorders', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:18:36', '2016-02-25 12:18:36', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=407', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(408, 1, '2016-02-25 12:18:48', '2016-02-25 12:18:48', 'Online Proof: Our online proof is there to give you an idea what your tickets will look like. If you’re not happy with the proof just tell us to send an actual proof (Our Artists have a lot more flexibility then the online proofing). If you’re adding a logo there is no need to request a proof. In either case complete your order and you will receive a proof the next business day.', 'Online Proof', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'online-proof', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:18:48', '2016-02-25 12:18:48', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=408', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(409, 1, '2016-02-25 12:19:00', '2016-02-25 12:19:00', 'Starting number for raffle tickets: Unless you specify otherwise they will start at 001. You can specify to begin at 000 (lottery raffles) or any thousand increments such as 2001 or 3,001, etc. If reordering, specify the starting number in the “comments” section.', 'Starting number for raffle tickets', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'starting-number-for-raffle-tickets', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:19:00', '2016-02-25 12:19:00', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=409', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(410, 1, '2016-02-25 12:19:13', '2016-02-25 12:19:13', 'Post office Box Deliveries: UPS will not deliver to Post Office Boxes. We can, however ship your raffle tickets via U.S. Priority mail. The charge for priority mail is $5.00 per 1000 raffle tickets. Add the appropriate charge in the box: “Price for Additional Services add to my order”.', 'Post office Box Deliveries', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'post-office-box-deliveries', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:19:13', '2016-02-25 12:19:13', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=410', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(411, 1, '2016-02-25 12:19:27', '2016-02-25 12:19:27', 'Track Shipping: You will receive an email with a tracking number the day your order is shipped.\r\n', 'Track Shipping', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'track-shipping', '', '', '2016-02-25 12:19:27', '2016-02-25 12:19:27', '', 0, 'http://www.raffle.dev/?post_type=faq&#038;p=411', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
